          <p>The Campaign for Senate series includes position papers outlining the Romney campaign's
            platform as well as a well-researched investigation into the record of her opponent,
            Phil Hart. Included are newspaper clippings collected by the campaign staff for a
            scrapbook (which apparently was never compiled) detailing the candidate's life during
            the campaign.</p>
